[Note: Further information can be found on the capitalized words by using the
HELP-command]

1.  Getting started.

When you enter the game you are graciously given a number of
practices.  These practices can be used to learn spells and
skills, or to increase your fundamental stats (strength, wisdom,
intelligence, dexterity, and constitution).

Many people that the best move is to use your initial practices
to study wisdom.  This is done at the fitness center.  At the
Guild you can ADVANCE and practice spells and skills.  To get
to the Guild go SSWWSSE from the Temple.  To get to the Fitness
center head SSWWSSW.

